newArticles.title: Minneapolis Teachers Announce They Will Go on Strike - The New York Times
newArticles.description: The union is asking for smaller class sizes and higher wages, while the school district says its budget is shrinking because of declining enrollment. After negotiations, St. Paul averted a strike.
